snippet.title: TAGLINE - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
TAGLINE a lightning fast, graffiti based shooter set in a loud, wild world sprinkled with street art, hip-hop, and towering skyscrapers. Snatch tags off the walls of this funky metropolis to overcome an array of enemies and challenges! 

Our development team is working to add new content, maps, enemies and more to the world of TAGLINE. We've got a long road ahead as we work on the game, and we'd love to hear your thoughts! Feel free to follow us for updates and wishlist our game on Steam! : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1921470/TAGLINE/
